suncertify.db
Interface DataInterface

All Superinterfaces:
java.rmi.Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:
Database, RemoteDataImpl
public interface DataInterface
extends java.rmi.Remote

This interface provides the basic services to be implemented by the connections access the datafile at the non-network or network mode

Version:
1.2 16-Nov-2002
Author:
Francisco Carlos
